      "date": "2014-12-01 08:51:38.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nThis patch should only land to b2_5 together with http://review.whamcloud.com/12723 since it is otherwise too noisy and prints a message even when the max_sectors_kb tunable is not changing.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
